    "While prior research has shown that machine learning algorithms can predict a person's psychological profile from their digital footprints (e.g.",
    "19, 20) the present work showcases how algorithms can now also design messages that appeal to these traits-even when given very limited input.",
    "In other words, current technologies, which continue to innovate and improve, have the potential to allow message sources to fully \"close the loop\" on automating personalized persuasion.",
    "In short, one of the most powerful forms of behavioral influence now has the potential to be implemented at scale.",
    "Companies, for example, could set up fully automated processes that leverage AI to execute sophisticated personalized marketing at scale."
